name: The Management
description:
The Federal College of Education (Technical) Bichi was established in 1986 and started full operation in 1987 with the aim of producing qualified, technical and vocational oriented teachers. It is a college for excellence that went through different stages of development and progress, it offer relevant courses and programs of NCE and Degree levels and provides Vocational/Technical services. 
I will like to invite you to experience our excellent academic activities.

Since its conversion to a polytechnic in 1989, Nuhu 
Bamalli Polytechnic has progressively developed in infrastructure, 
staffing and students enrolment. Presently, there are 46 academic 
programmes in 31 departments (including IJMB and Basic and Remedial) 
training students for the award of Diploma, National Diploma, Higher 
National Diploma and National Certificate of Education. There are seven 
(7) schools with 31 departments viz:
